- Always use strong typing in `.ts` / `.tsx` files; avoid `any`.
- For icons in JSX, use `react-icons` instead of emoji.
- Run lint and fix all warnings/errors after each task.
- Database migration filenames must include a unique current timestamp.
- Dont user alert to provide feedback, need to using right confirmation dialog
- Break large React components into smaller ones:
  - If reusable across pages → move to shared components folder.
  - If used only on one page → keep in that page’s folder.